=== CUBOID BRICK AT n=4 ===
H=5 at n=4: 24 tournaments. All have t₃=2, sharing 2 vertices.
Ω = K_2 (complete graph on 2 vertices)
I(K_2, x) = 1 + 2x → I(K_2, 2) = 5 = H ✓
This IS the cuboid brick!

